<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-537] Lustre Wiki: Review Robinhood Policy Engine Page</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-537</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following pages are all over 3 years old.&#160; These are being reviewed as part of the efforts of the Lustre Documentation Working Group.&#160; The main intent of this bug is to evaluate if these pages require:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Reorganization&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Removal due to staleness&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Extension due to missing material&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Correction to fix incorrect or stale material&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;The author is expected to annotate this work item with the changes expected.&#160; They may or may not make those changes as part of this work item.&#160; If they choose to not make those changes, they are expected to create a new work item where the identified, explicit improvements can be made by another individual within the LUDOC stream.&#160; If they do choose to make those changes, please clarify such in the comment section.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The full list of pages include:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000080&quot;&gt;[&lt;font color=&quot;#0645ad&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;Robinhood Policy Engine&lt;/font&gt;|https://wiki.lustre.org/Robinhood_Policy_Engine]&lt;font color=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#202122&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&#8207;&#8206; (09:47, 24 May 2016)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
